

<p> Search for a flickr user (and some of their photos) using their ID:</p>

<br>
If you don't know the id, type the user's home page in at this address:
<br>
http://idgettr.com/
<br>

<%= form_tag("/", method: "get") do %>
  <%= text_field_tag(:id) %>
  <%= submit_tag("Search") %>
<% end %>

<br><br>



